### schedule() {#a72b9c4f9a9fe8ef321b387a3cfca73cd}

<MemberDefinition
  prototype="void DefaultVLIWScheduler::schedule ()"
  labels = {["virtual"]}>
Orders nodes according to selected style.

Typically, a scheduling algorithm will implement <a href="#a72b9c4f9a9fe8ef321b387a3cfca73cd">schedule()</a> without overriding <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/scheduledaginstrs/#ae8727d434d20639d563849891f5ca1e1">enterRegion()</a> or <a href="/docs/api/classes/llvm/scheduledaginstrs/#abc5a5c32ac78a99ee2633dbbeec20397">exitRegion()</a>.
